        Get reviews of a specfic company:<br>
        GET http://35.226.176.140/api/reviews/#CompanyId
        <br><br><br>


        Save a review for a company:<br>
        POST http://35.226.176.140/api/reviews
        <br>
        Body:
        <br>{
        <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Review: "review",
        <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;User: "user name",
        <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;Rating: 3,
        <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;CompanyId: 1
        <br>}
